what a crazy few years it’s been but i wouldn’t change any of it. being a mom has taught me so many different things, but the thing it’s taught me the most is to never take a moment for granted. it is true that time flies. one minute im holding my newborn baby boy and the next thing i know i see him cheering in the stands for me like a big boy. 

pregnancy is hard, recovery from birth is hard, finding and learning to love yourself again is hard, being a mom is freaking hard, but my goodness it is SO WORTH IT and the BEST thing in the world. i love being your mama baby zee. 

happy mother’s day to all the amazing mommy’s out there!🤍🤍
